      "description": "The Truth Social American Red State REITs ETF (TSRS) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in real estate equity. The fund is passively managed to provide exposure to US REITs that derive their revenues from states that have voted for a Republican presidential candidate. The portfolio is market-cap weighted. TSRS was launched on Dec 30, 2025 and is issued by Truth Social.",
